title: 5 Things I Wish I Learned In Hair School
description: Hair school is a special time in every stylist's life but it can be scary that first day you're on your own and even scarier when you don't feel fully equipped to take on the professional hairdresser world! We imagine that this is a pretty standard issue whether you went to hair school or business school. Today we sit down with fellow stylist Kaylee and talk about the 5 things we wish we would have learned in hair school!
